* Karzai is well-versed in [[Pushtu language|Pushtu]], [[Dari (of Afghanistan)|Dari]], [[Urdu language|Urdu]], [[Hindi language|Hindi]], [[Persian language|Persian]], [[English language|English]] and [[French language|French]] languages. 

