* On [[May 21]], [[2005]], he was denied permission to throw a ceremonial first pitch at a [[Boston Red Sox]] game at [[Fenway Park]], due to security and logistical concerns.

* On May 25, 2005, he visited a [[West Point, Nebraska]] cattle feeder, and received an honorary degree from the Center for Afghan Studies at the [[University of Nebraska]] - Omaha.

